{"article_id":"SPUkNPmLs1X42ekq","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Former US President Barack Obama has attacked the Trump administration","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"for scrapping his scheme","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"to protect young undocumented migrants from deportation .","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"The Deferred Action for Childhood Arrivals","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"( Daca )","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"programme was rescinded on Tuesday , in a move","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"that could affect some 800,000 beneficiaries .","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"While existing recipients will see no impact for at least six months ,","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"no new applications can now be made .","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"Appealing to Congress ,","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"Mr Obama said","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"the decision was `` cruel '' and `` wrong '' .","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"The so-called `` Dreamers '' , mostly Latin Americans , were able to apply for work and study permits under the policy","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"he introduced five years ago .","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"The Trump administration argues","depth":4},{"id":15,"text":"that the programme ,","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"which Mr Obama bypassed Congress","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"in order to enact ,","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"was unconstitutional ,","depth":5},{"id":19,"text":"In a tweet , President Donald Trump , said","depth":5},{"id":20,"text":"he now looked forward to working with both Democrats and Republicans in Congress","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"to `` address immigration reform in a way","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"that puts hardworking citizens of our country 1st '' .","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"`` Congress now has 6 months to legalize DACA","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"( something","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"the Obama Administration was unable to do ) .","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"If they ca n't ,","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"I will revisit this issue ! ''","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"he added , in a second tweet .","depth":5},{"id":29,"text":"Police in New York made at least a dozen arrests","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"when protesters rallied in front of Trump Tower ,","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"US media report ,","depth":5},{"id":32,"text":"but there were no reports of clashes .","depth":4},{"id":33,"text":"Candidate Trump promised to do away with Daca ,","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"despite warnings from a cross-party collection of politicians .","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"Or ,","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"knowing this president ,","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"objections from `` the establishment '' only make him more determined to act .","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"Fortunately for him ,","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"unlike repealing Obamacare or building his Mexican border wall ,","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"he does not need Congress 's help here .","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"In fact ,","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"by setting a six-month fuse on the effects of Daca 's termination","depth":12},{"id":43,"text":"- and stretching the impact out over the next two years","depth":13},{"id":44,"text":"as work permits expire -","depth":13},{"id":45,"text":"Mr Trump puts all the pressure on legislators .","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"It will not be easy for Daca supporters in Congress .","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"They will have to get legislation passed over the objection of immigration hawks in the House .","depth":12},{"id":48,"text":"It may also need 60 votes in the Senate","depth":14},{"id":49,"text":"to break a filibuster ,","depth":14},{"id":50,"text":"if the bill is packaged with hardline immigration measures .","depth":13},{"id":51,"text":"What is more , Congress already has its hands full with other pressing issues","depth":12},{"id":52,"text":"- hurricane relief , budget resolutions , the need","depth":13},{"id":53,"text":"to authorise new government debt and , at some point , tax reform .","depth":13},{"id":54,"text":"If Congress fails to act ,","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"Republicans with tough re-election races will be in a difficult spot ,","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"facing angry constituents","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"just as the campaign season gets into gear .","depth":12},{"id":58,"text":"The president , however , satisfies his anti-immigration base with this move","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"- and washes his hands of the matter .","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"The loyalists","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"who have stood by him","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"are rewarded ,","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"others in his party be damned .","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"Mr Obama wrote on Facebook :","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"`` To target these young people is wrong -","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"because they have done nothing wrong . ''","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"`` Ultimately , this is about basic decency , ''","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"he said .","depth":12},{"id":69,"text":"`` This is about whether we are a people","depth":13},{"id":70,"text":"who kick hopeful young strivers out of America ,","depth":13},{"id":71,"text":"or whether we treat them the way","depth":13},{"id":72,"text":"we 'd want our own kids to be treated . ''","depth":13},{"id":73,"text":"Despite bypassing Congress himself over the issue ,","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"the former president said :","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"`` Now that the White House has shifted its responsibility for these young people to Congress ,","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"it 's up to members of Congress to protect these young people and our future . ''","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"In a statement , House Democratic leader Nancy Pelosi also slammed Tuesday 's decision","depth":7},{"id":78,"text":"and called on majority Republicans in Congress to join Democrats","depth":8},{"id":79,"text":"in immediately moving to safeguard Daca recipients .","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"Two senators from the opposing parties held a joint news conference","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"to call for bipartisan legislation","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"to protect Dreamers .","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"`` The clock is ticking , ''","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"Democrat Dick Durbin said ,","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"while Republican Lindsey Graham said :","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"`` We believe","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"in doing it right","depth":11},{"id":88,"text":"but 'right ' means taking care of these kids . ''","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"The Mexican government said in a statement","depth":6},{"id":90,"text":"( in Spanish )","depth":6},{"id":91,"text":"that it profoundly regretted the scrapping of Daca","depth":6},{"id":92,"text":"and would step up its consular work on behalf of its citizens","depth":7},{"id":93,"text":"who are affected .","depth":7},{"id":94,"text":"Mr Trump took a hard line on immigration","depth":6},{"id":95,"text":"while campaigning last year","depth":6},{"id":96,"text":"and promised to scrap Daca","depth":6},{"id":97,"text":"if elected .","depth":6},{"id":98,"text":"In a statement , he said","depth":5},{"id":99,"text":"he did not `` favour punishing children ,","depth":8},{"id":100,"text":"most of whom are now adults ,","depth":8},{"id":101,"text":"for the actions of their parents '' .","depth":7},{"id":102,"text":"`` But we must also recognise","depth":8},{"id":103,"text":"that we are nation of opportunity","depth":9},{"id":104,"text":"because we are a nation of laws , ''","depth":9},{"id":105,"text":"he added .","depth":7},{"id":106,"text":"The scrapping of Daca was announced on Tuesday by Attorney General Jeff Sessions","depth":5},{"id":107,"text":"who described Mr Obama 's policy as an `` open-ended circumvention of immigration laws '' .","depth":5},{"id":108,"text":"`` There can be no path to principled immigration reform","depth":6},{"id":109,"text":"if the executive branch is able to rewrite or nullify federal laws at will , ''","depth":6},{"id":110,"text":"Mr Trump said .","depth":5},{"id":111,"text":"No new first-time requests will be acted on after 5 September ,","depth":7},{"id":112,"text":"Department of Homeland Security","depth":9},{"id":113,"text":"( DHS )","depth":9},{"id":114,"text":"Acting Secretary Elaine Duke said in a memo","depth":9},{"id":115,"text":"released","depth":10},{"id":116,"text":"after Mr Sessions spoke .","depth":10},{"id":117,"text":"However , no existing beneficiaries of the policy will feel any impact for six months , the period of time","depth":7},{"id":118,"text":"allotted for Congress","depth":8},{"id":119,"text":"to `` deliver on appropriate legislative solutions '' .","depth":8},{"id":120,"text":"People","depth":8},{"id":121,"text":"who have current Daca work authorisation","depth":8},{"id":122,"text":"will be able to keep it","depth":8},{"id":123,"text":"until it expires","depth":8},{"id":124,"text":"while people","depth":8},{"id":125,"text":"whose permits expire in less than six months","depth":8},{"id":126,"text":"can renew before 1 October for another full two years .","depth":7},{"id":127,"text":"In order to qualify for Daca ,","depth":6},{"id":128,"text":"applicants under the age of 30 had to submit personal information to the DHS .","depth":6},{"id":129,"text":"They had to go through an FBI background check","depth":7},{"id":130,"text":"and have a clean criminal record ,","depth":8},{"id":131,"text":"and either be in school ,","depth":9},{"id":132,"text":"have recently graduated","depth":10},{"id":133,"text":"or have been honourably discharged from the military .","depth":10},{"id":134,"text":"In exchange , the US government agreed to defer any action on their immigration status for a period of two years .","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":269,"left":167,"right":268,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":167,"left":153,"right":166,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":153,"left":148,"right":152,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":148,"left":137,"right"